wiki.summary: “Prices” features Uzi in a very braggadocios manner, claiming his money, fame, and overall “price” are going up. The track was first teased by producer Brandon Finessin’s on his Instagram Live video on March 2, 2020. Later, fans got confirmation that the track would appear on Eternal Atake after a snippet of its instrumental was played in the album’s short film Baby Pluto. The track samples the instrumental from the second half of Travis Scott’s September 2016 track “way back,” which was produced by Cashmere Cat. Read more on Last.fm.
